.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一早有散既諗法 有曬心理準備 但係都好似硬係少左野咁   散完好平淡 但又好心酸 sorry我語無倫次<br />\n年齡問題 大家分享既樂悅好難感同身受  我毒撚仔覺得自己阻住佢咁 佢係一個好女仔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c7acefcf35b74b0c9567796e8bc8aebbf3ad46e","tid":258090,"uid":4422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T19:11:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>介紹個女仔黎識下</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好女仔唔可以亂介紹 見一個少一個"},{"pid":"252e3c29ab9ea5640421c7aa58423ad8eb76e68d","tid":258090,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T19:13:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下個更可愛呢d呀媽都知嘅野唔多講啦<br />\n咪當個經驗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實咩事散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一早有散既諗法 有曬心理準備 但係都好似硬係少左野咁   散完好平淡 但又好心酸 sorry我語無倫次<br />\n年齡問題 大家分享既樂悅好難感同身受  我毒撚仔覺得自己阻住佢咁 佢係一個好女仔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n差3年炸喎 你今年中一媾左個小學生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5e4a05332441433e30660133e241bc8515d109","tid":258090,"uid":4422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T19:13:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鬧你都要原因啦<br />\n<br />\n唔好講d唔講d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我大佢太多 所以好多代溝 我笑咩佢唔明 佢笑咩我又唔明 共同話題太少 有努力去發掘過 不過維持唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b7e48b218447b4e3077898b3cbd9d9dc6b44a7","tid":258090,"uid":4422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T19:14:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>下個更可愛呢d呀媽都知嘅野唔多講啦<br />\n咪當個經驗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實咩事散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一早有散既諗法 有曬心理準備 但係都好似硬係少左野咁   散完好平淡 但又好心酸 sorry我語無倫次<br />\n年齡問題 大家分享既樂悅好難感同身受  我毒撚仔覺得自己阻住佢咁 佢係一個好女仔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n差3年炸喎 你今年中一媾左個小學生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n出黎做野既話三年唔係問題  讀緊書就好大分別啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49540c4e0682d7800cebb82bc015a7be8fd58e14","tid":258090,"uid":7764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T19:21:34.000Z","msg":"三年好小事啫⋯⋯反而要了解對方諗咩先重點"},{"pid":"a5bd973c73202addaeb643b6f641743242e96d9f","tid":258090,"uid":52819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T19:25:02.000Z","msg":"五年 訓唔著 聽日番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eab84f7ea738aae46d9ec51b93261e0614a7b6d","tid":258090,"uid":4422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T19:26:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三年好小事啫⋯⋯反而要了解對方諗咩先重點</blockquote><br />\n當你考完dse佢先中三 你讀完hd/大學佢先考完dse/year1      唔覺好大差距咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f94704efde5789776208101178f682c6dfb40c74","tid":258090,"uid":4422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T19:26:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>五年 訓唔著 聽日番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打搞咩"},{"pid":"a0ccc3dcf2edea04eb5935dfaf03c60491bc013c","tid":258090,"uid":43544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T19:30:17.000Z","msg":"想講分手 唔知點開口<br />\n利申：同居"},{"pid":"d7c684f78404a46e9f445b3a9644731d76b31d81","tid":258090,"uid":25452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T19:32:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>三年好小事啫⋯⋯反而要了解對方諗咩先重點</blockquote><br />\n當你考完dse佢先中三 你讀完hd/大學佢先考完dse/year1      唔覺好大差距咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你拍拖姐 <br />\n唔好講到好似係要留班一齊同個班房讀書咁<br />\n唔係同級仲好啦 你估日見夜見真係好sweet咩<br />\n曾經有個朋友中一 溝左個中六嘅  吹水仆街死<br />\n最後都係因為偷吃散姐 <br />\n因為年齡你唔覺好牽強咩 仲要得3年唔係30年"},{"pid":"5fd90d87283678443d4c798c289d6535c9ab5341","tid":258090,"uid":4422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T19:33:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想講分手 唔知點開口<br />\n利申：同居</blockquote><br />\n介唔介意講下 可能大家幫到你呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}